title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 11 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 11 2022
description:
Video of SF kids walking through sea of homeless shocks the nation. New video emerges exonerating NYC bodega worker charged with murder by DA Alvin Bragg for defending himself. Biden says the Parkland shooting happened in 1918. Former House Speaker Newt Gingrich joins Clay and Buck to discuss Biden and his new book: Defeating Big Government Socialism: Saving America's Future. They're going to be telling you to get more shots. Will Manchin deliver Biden a new spending bill? Biden goes to Saudi Arabia to beg for oil. Biden DOJ to investigate PGA Tour.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
